OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782134325
OL,3,CCornwall woman is first in Europe to
OL,4,Ctake part in new blood cancer trial
OL,6,FA Cornwall patient has become the
OL,7,Ffirst person in Europe to take part in
OL,8,Fa new drug trial for blood cancer.
OL,10,FVanessa Maule has been undergoing a
OL,11,Fnew type of treatment at the Royal
OL,12,FCornwall Hospitals NHS Trust designed
OL,13,Fto help the body's own immune system
OL,14,Ffind and destroy myeloma cells.
OL,16,FThe LINKER study is using a drug
OL,17,Fcalled linvoseltamab, which works by
OL,18,Fbringing cancer cells and immune cells
OL,19,Ftogether so the body can target the
OL,20,Fdisease more effectively.
