PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782134325
OL,3,CCornwall woman is first in Europe to
OL,4,Ctake part in new blood cancer trial
OL,6,FVanessa was diagnosed with myeloma in
OL,7,F2023 following severe back and rib
OL,8,Fpain.
OL,10,FShe explained: "I was told I had an
OL,11,Fincurable but highly treatable form of
OL,12,Fblood cancer and started treatment
OL,13,Falmost immediately. In 2025, I was on
OL,14,Fthe road to recovery; back at work,
OL,15,Ftravelling and taking part in a
OL,16,Fcharity coast path walk with friends
OL,17,Ffor Myeloma Awareness Week."
OL,26,@rD@POUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782134325
OL,3,CCornwall woman is first in Europe to
OL,4,Ctake part in new blood cancer trial
OL,6,FA PET scan in February 2026 confirmed
OL,7,Fthat the myeloma was active again, and
OL,8,Fthe LINKER trial became available as
OL,9,FVanessa was discussing treatment
OL,10,Foptions.
OL,12,FShe said: "It was really disappointing
OL,13,Fto get the news that it was active
OL,14,Fagain, but I was encouraged by feeling
OL,15,Fwell in myself, and there was no
OL,16,Fhesitation about being part of the
OL,17,Ftrial. I felt positive about the
OL,18,Fpromising effects of the medication,
OL,19,Fdespite also knowing there were some
OL,20,Finitial risks.
OL,26,@tD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782134325
OL,3,CCornwall woman is first in Europe to
OL,4,Ctake part in new blood cancer trial
OL,6,F"I have been well-informed and looked
OL,7,Fafter and have a great deal of trust
OL,8,Fin the Haematology Team. The drug has
OL,9,Falready been used in US myeloma
OL,10,Ftreatment, so the trial factor was
OL,11,Fhaving access to it earlier. I was
OL,12,Fsurprised when I heard I was the first
OL,13,Fpatient to be treated in Europe. I
OL,14,Ffeel so lucky, and it's mind-boggling
OL,15,Fto know that some of my blood goes off
OL,16,Fto labs in Edinburgh and Switzerland.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782134325
OL,3,CCornwall woman is first in Europe to
OL,4,Ctake part in new blood cancer trial
OL,6,F"It was so fortuitous that this trial
OL,7,Fcame along just as I needed more
OL,8,Ftreatment. It's great that there is
OL,9,Fcutting-edge medicine available in
OL,10,FCornwall, and that the research team
OL,11,Fworks so relentlessly to secure these
OL,12,Fopportunities."
OL,14,FShe added: "I feel proud being part of
OL,15,Fthe trial; knowing that the data
OL,16,Fgathered about me and my myeloma can
OL,17,Fhelp other patients in the future
OL,18,Fgives me hope because having myeloma
OL,19,Fmeans you want to live well with the
OL,20,Fdisease for as long as you can."
OL,26,@nD@AOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
