FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1782134325
OL,3,CCornwall woman is first in Europe to
OL,4,Ctake part in new blood cancer trial
OL,6,FDenise Storey, Senior Research Nurse
OL,7,Fat RCHT, said: "We're proud to be
OL,8,Fplaying such an important role in
OL,9,Finternational research with the first
OL,10,Fpatient in Europe joining this study
OL,11,Fhere in Cornwall.
OL,13,F"Research like this wouldn't happen
OL,14,Fwithout patients who are willing to
OL,15,Ftake part, and it's inspiring to see
OL,16,Four patients, like Vanessa, helping
OL,17,Fmove treatment forward, not just for
OL,18,Fthemselves, but for others in the
OL,19,Ffuture."
OL,26,@oD@POUuD@AOU{D@HO]
